name: Hawa Cat is a Francophile
description: Hawa Cat has put on her Bengal cat outfit and visiting Paris. She loves Paris and anything French. She is practicing her French and goes to the cinema. Hawa Cat is an artist. She spends the morning painting and goes to the Louvre in the afternoon. She loves Paris because its a city that has always loved and revered artists and creativity. Add to that the delicious food!! She's looking for Remi of Ratatouille. She's reading "My Life in France" by Julia Child, its one of her favorite books ever. She walks the streets day and night and spends magical moments in the ancient churches.
